flowchart LR
    subgraph PRIMARY[Site primaire]
      APP1[Applications] --> RAC1[RAC sur Exadata primaire]
      RAC1 --> DATA1[(DATA/RECO ASM)]
    end
    subgraph STANDBY[Site standby]
      RAC2[RAC ou SI sur Exadata standby] --> DATA2[(DATA/RECO ASM)]
    end
    RAC1 -- Redo transport --> RAC2
    BROKER[Data Guard Broker] --> RAC1
    BROKER --> RAC2
    RMAN[RMAN Backups] --> DATA1
    RMAN --> DATA2
